SELECT
    db_bctl_rgno   AS rgno,
    db_bctl_area   AS area,
    db_bctl_brno   AS brno,
    db_bctl_boff   AS boff,
    db_bctl_micr   AS micr,
    db_bctl_frex   AS frex,
    db_bctl_rtolbr AS rtolbr,
    db_bctl_brname AS brname,
    db_bctl_monbr  AS monbr,
    CASE
        WHEN db_bctl_class IS NULL
             OR isnumeric(db_bctl_class) = 0 THEN
            0
        ELSE
            db_bctl_class
    END            AS class,
    db_bctl_seq    AS seq,
    db_bctl_arcd   AS arcd,
    CASE
        WHEN nullif(db_bctl_zipcd, '') IS NULL THEN
            '    '
        ELSE
            db_bctl_zipcd
    END            AS zipcd,
    db_bctl_chcd   AS chcd,
    db_bctl_chnam  AS chnam
FROM
    botsrdb.db_bctl_dds
WHERE
    db_bctl_brno < 990
